<h4><a name="fletching">Part 6: Fletching</a></h4> 
<p><b>Skill Requirement:</b> (220 Fletching assumed).</p> 
<p><b>Flag Requirement</b>: Rallos Zek and Solusek Ro?</p> 
<p><b>Commentary:</b> <i>None, as of yet.</i></p> 
<p>Original text:</p>
<blockquote> 
<p>You say, 'I am skilled with a fletching knife'</p>
<p>Aid Grimel says 'Aye I can see you are skilled with the fletching knife ____. It is good too, I need to replace Councilman Taldarius's bow from Plane of Air. Combine a planing tool, two wind metal bow cams, an air arachnid silk string, a featherwood staff and the signet. I hope the bow will be up to his standards, he sure loved his old bow.'</p>
</blockquote> 
<p>Return to him with the signet featherwood bow in order to receive the runed signet</p> 
